{"tid":1356191,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[727] 2019最新歌謠 《何家仆街何家猜》","createTime":"2019-07-23T12:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T07:02:53.000Z","uid":34415,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3b90eb611c4b3b0dbe7e8b12fbd4d0c945010698","tid":1356191,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:33:09.000Z","msg":"《何家仆街何家猜》<br />\n真怪誕呀又有趣　你望望龕塚裡 <br />\n有伯母副仙骨咯咯咯　是何家的親生母<br />\n <br />\n何家仆街何家猜　何家子孫何仆街 <br />\n何家仆街何家猜　何家母親墳倒了<br />\n <br />\n南邊叔父何先生　同班黑幫齊嘻哈<br />\n酬金不足煩媽媽　娘親墳起了<br />\n<br />\n727可以一齊唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原link有人唱埋你聽:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2367382879985917&amp;id=1633893760001503\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2367382879985917%26id%3D1633893760001503&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4filxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=a937363c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2367382879985917&amp;id=1633893760001503</a>"},{"pid":"8fd7c63ecf6eb96c6ccdb7b04fa0cfb1daae5bb3","tid":1356191,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:34:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />727 元朗反恐<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e34decd3d1bb6ebef186cc121fc7277827a6ed2","tid":1356191,"uid":34415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:34:48.000Z","msg":"上環片整合：<br />\n<br />\n1.【721回顧 | 警察先主動進攻 狂射催淚彈橡膠彈】 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D341910530087022&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4filxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=98689217\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022</a><br />\n2. 23:34 於永安中心外，示威者呼籲全部人「一齊走」。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D347322312837536&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4filxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=ad467a8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536</a><br />\n3.【721即時】 22:44 警察向示威者開槍。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D336543320631999&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4filxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=7fb6441e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999</a><br />\n4. 【721即時】22:38 在示威者推進途中，警方突然向人群射出催淚彈，及急速推進。示威者向警方投擲雜物還擊，警方再發射多枚催淚彈。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D436610810398685&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4filxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=332876a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685</a><br />\n5. 【721即時】 22:12 港澳碼頭外，警察向示威者施放胡椒噴霧。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D497139927720468&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4filxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=7b9e406d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468</a><br />\n6. 【721即時】 22:00 干諾道西港澳碼頭外警察突然推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2450364665024731&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4filxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=18864295\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731</a><br />\n7. 21:20 警察以「一二一二」的口令由德輔道西向西邊街推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1310939165740421&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4filxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=5801b767\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421</a><br />\n8. 20:55 中區警署外的示威者向警署外牆掉油漆彈、磚頭及腐蝕性液體 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D725595331211578&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4filxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=3e72447c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578</a><br />\n9. 20:23 有一批全black bloc的警員不斷推進防線，惟沒有委任證及證明文件。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D406909290170265&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4filxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=67c69bed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265</a><br />\n10. 20:13 示威者現正由干諾道西向後奔跑至德輔道西。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D789204521474060&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4filxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=79bbac6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060</a><br />\n11. 上環清場中 警方對這個用身體阻擋催淚彈的男人這樣處理<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAzZoteAvCyw&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4filxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=a3a56a41\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw</a> <br />\n12. 示威者疑中槍倒地 同伴築防線助急救 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2433207320290299&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4filxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=e34abf6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299</a><br />\n13. 2019/0721/上環硝煙花特別多<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBpfKm3Ls34U%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4f